name: SXZ Illidari Demon Hunters [ Warcraft ]
description:
All the content I make is and will be completely free on CivitAI.
But if you want to support me with a coin, then you can do it here.

Trained on AbyssOrangeMix2 with Clip Skip 2.

Sample images was generated with Luma and AOM2

Recommended embeddings:
1. easynegative
2. bad-hands-5
3. badhandv4

Strength 0.6-0.8 is optimal.

PLEASE CHECK YOUR LORA NAME AFTER DOWNLOAD.

Male Illidari: 1boy, illidari
Female Illidari: 1girl, illidari

Skin color: any, but you can go with purple skin if you want to make Illidan
Eye color: any, but also you may use glowing green eyes, blindfold

Also you may improve it with wings, horns, muscular, glowing eyes, tattoo
